2026-05-17T00:28:02.0297969Z 13    <!--
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0298702Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0299925Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0301304Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0302357Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0303469Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
