2026-05-17T00:28:02.0309452Z 22    <!--
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0310185Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0311067Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0311898Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0312873Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0313839Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0314801Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0316531Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0317553Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0318532Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0319641Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0320406Z 33    -->
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0321193Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-05-17T00:28:02.0322370Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:5-79
