2026-05-17T00:28:02.4984086Z 20-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/build/intermediates/tmp/manifest/test/debug/tempFile2ProcessTestManifest15648945371364615608.xml:21:22-78
2026-05-17T00:28:02.4984242Z 21    <!--
2026-05-17T00:28:02.4984601Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-17T00:28:02.4984802Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-17T00:28:02.4985146Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-17T00:28:02.4985462Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-17T00:28:02.4985784Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-17T00:28:02.4986082Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-17T00:28:02.4986408Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-17T00:28:02.4986723Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-17T00:28:02.4987020Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-17T00:28:02.4987286Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-17T00:28:02.4987439Z 32    -->
2026-05-17T00:28:02.4987839Z 33    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-05-17T00:28:02.4988740Z 33-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/build/intermediates/tmp/manifest/test/debug/tempFile2ProcessTestManifest15648945371364615608.xml:34:5-79
